{"tid":665483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［年經］一人一件覺得你朋友好嘔心嘅事","createTime":"2018-05-15T04:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T19:19:04.000Z","uid":105159,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cfcd30dd3858116283c173acb732c76b9fbac033","tid":665483,"uid":105159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:02:50.000Z","msg":"我拋磚引玉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說上年夏天我啱啱返新工<br />\n咁嗰度有位同事就少少肥同大汗既<br />\n由於佢既工作不時都會外出<br />\n所以返嚟既時候佢都會濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但奇就奇在佢每次件衫乾返之後個肚既位置都會出現一條白色野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁當時既我就冇乜理會始終唔係太熟<br />\n而且冬天既時候又冇再出現過<br />\n但直至宜家夏天又再出現返<br />\n咁見都同佢熟咗於是我就忍唔住問佢<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   同事：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：喂 其實我想問你樣嘢好耐<br />\n同事：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：點解你個肚有啲白色嘢喺度嘅？<br />\n同事：哦！呢啲鹽嚟架！<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仆街我認我無知見識少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前仲多手走去掂佢啲人體鍊成既鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你哋又有冇相關嘅經歷分享下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd46405eb43b1c7f3022fee84a20418c768ba7e5","tid":665483,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:05:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"355a008802656e0f4f6469488b89230b43f9ff4c","tid":665483,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":67,"score":-67,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"點解次次打邊爐咁做, d friend都會覺得我怪<br />\n身為香港人，一年四季打邊爐是常識吧<br />\n次次打緊邊爐自己個碗一定愈黎愈多湯渣同水之類<br />\n咁我慣左一多就會倒番落個爐度<br />\n佢地話我核突<br />\n其實有咩咁怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4076fa6d4cc9a50d3231